    • appointments

      public static void appointments(List<Appointment> list, char key)
      Sort appointments based on a given key. The key can be used to decide sorting by date, timeslot, patient, or provider.
      Parameters:
      list - the list of appointments to sort.
      key - the key to determine the sorting criteria ('d' for date, 't' for timeslot, etc.).
